<h2>🎯 核心定义</h2>
<h3>1.1 七维度</h3>
<table>
<thead><tr>
<th>字母</th>
<th>英文</th>
<th>中文</th>
<th>核心问题</th>
</tr></thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>S</strong></td>
<td>Substitute</td>
<td>替代</td>
<td>能否用其他来替代？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>C</strong></td>
<td>Combine</td>
<td>合并</td>
<td>能否与其他合并？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>A</strong></td>
<td>Adapt</td>
<td>调适/借用</td>
<td>能否从其他领域借鉴？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>M</strong></td>
<td>Modify/Magnify</td>
<td>修改/扩大</td>
<td>能否改变/放大？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>P</strong></td>
<td>Put to other uses</td>
<td>转用</td>
<td>能否用于其他目的？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>E</strong></td>
<td>Eliminate</td>
<td>消除/简化</td>
<td>能否消除或简化？</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>R</strong></td>
<td>Reverse/Rearrange</td>
<td>重组/反转</td>
<td>能否颠倒或重新安排？</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
